						<summary>

						<p>Fragment of a slab lying in the field of Vaḍla Basapa.</p>						

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1090,</hi> the other details are lost. The corresponding date is 1168 A.D. Much damaged. It refers to gifts of land. It also mentions Vīrayyaṅgāru.</p>						

